MGA Entertainment Seeks $130 Million From Mattel for Bratz Suit Legal Fees

-- B y   E d v a r d   P e t t e r s s o n
-- 
2011-05-24T02:30:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/mga-entertainment-seeks-130-million-from-mattel-for-bratz-suit-legal-fees.html
MGA Entertainment Inc. asked a judge
to order  Mattel Inc. (MAT)  to pay it $130 million in attorney fees
following a jury verdict that found MGA hadn’t infringed
Mattel’s copyrights and that Mattel was liable for stealing
MGA’s trade secrets.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edvard Pettersson in Los Angeles at 
 epettersson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Hytha at 
